author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
Skeletá - the latest album from Ghost - was released on April 25 and I was advised to listen to it on my run. I thought I'd share some of my thoughts about it with you. We haven't played the tracks in their entirety for this review - so if you want to listen first - visit Ghost here on YouTube: 
https://www.youtube.com/@thebandGhost
And if you have suggestions for other albums I should play on my run, leave me a comment. 

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

The new Darkness "Dreams On Toast" is available now: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/

Get a Justin Hawkins Rides Again T-Shirt & Hoodie here: https://thejawsofvictory

#reaction #musicreview  #ghost
title: Running with Ghost: Thoughts on Skeletá
